            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-12-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-01-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="892" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d892">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>At the afternoon meeting of the General Assembly on November 28, the French
                    Representative proposed that the Assembly postpone its decision until the
                    following day to permit a last-minute effort to arrive at a solution acceptable
                    to both the Arabs and the Jews. The French proposal was adopted by a vote of 25
                    to 15. For the official record of the discussion of the proposal, see <gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss> (II) <hi rend="italic">Plenary</hi>, pages
                    1401–1410, <hi rend="italic">passim</hi>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
